In [11]:
def get_stats(group):
    return {'min': group.min(), 'max': group.max(),
            'count': group.count(), 'mean': group.mean()}
In [12]:
airport_mean_delays = pd.DataFrame(pd.Series(df['ORIGIN'].unique()))
airport_mean_delays.set_index(0, drop = True, inplace = True)

for month in df['MONTH'].unique():
    df1 = df[df['MONTH'] == month]
    test = df1['DELAYED'].groupby(df1['ORIGIN']).apply(get_stats).unstack()
    airport_mean_delays[month] = test.loc[:, 'mean']
    
airport_mean_delays['year_mean'] = airport_mean_delays.mean(axis=1)
airport_mean_delays = airport_mean_delays.sort_values(by='year_mean', ascending=False)
airport_mean_delays = airport_mean_delays.dropna()

tabela = pd.DataFrame(data={'suma_lotow': df['CRS_DEP_TIME_CAT'].value_counts().sort_index().values,
                             'opoznione_loty': df['CRS_DEP_TIME_CAT'][df['DEP_DELAY'] > 10].value_counts().sort_index().values},
                       index=df['CRS_DEP_TIME_CAT'].value_counts().sort_index().index)
tabela['udzial'] = tabela['opoznione_loty']/tabela['suma_lotow']*100
tabela['sztuczne_loty'] = (tabela['suma_lotow']-tabela['opoznione_loty'])

tick = np.arange(24)

stats=np.array(tabela['udzial'].values.T)
stats=np.concatenate((stats,[stats[0]]))
stats1=np.array(tabela['suma_lotow'].values.T)
stats1=np.concatenate((stats1,[stats1[0]]))
angles=np.linspace(0, 2*np.pi, len(tick), endpoint=False)
angles=np.concatenate((angles,[angles[0]]))
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(14,8))
fig.suptitle('Flights over the day', fontsize=16)
ax1 = fig.add_subplot(1,2,1, polar=True)
ax1.bar(angles, stats, width=(2*np.pi) / 23, color='red', alpha=0.5)
ax1.set_thetagrids(angles * 180/np.pi, tick)
ax1.set_title('Percentage of delayed flights')
ax1.set_theta_zero_location("N")
ax1.set_theta_direction(-1)
ax2 = fig.add_subplot(1,2,2, polar=True)
ax2.bar(angles, stats1, width=(2*np.pi) / 23, alpha=0.5)
ax2.set_thetagrids(angles * 180/np.pi, tick)
ax2.set_title('Sum of flights')
ax2.set_theta_zero_location("N")
ax2.set_theta_direction(-1)

tabela = pd.DataFrame(data={'suma_lotow': df['OP_UNIQUE_CARRIER'].value_counts().sort_index().values,
                         'opoznione_loty': df['OP_UNIQUE_CARRIER'][df['DEP_DELAY'] > 10].value_counts().sort_index().values},
                   index=df['OP_UNIQUE_CARRIER'].value_counts().sort_index().index)
tabela['udzial'] = tabela['opoznione_loty']/tabela['suma_lotow']*100
tabela['sztuczne_loty'] = (tabela['suma_lotow']-tabela['opoznione_loty'])
#tabela = tabela.sort_values(by='suma_lotow')
N = tabela.shape[0]
loty = tabela['sztuczne_loty']
opoznienie = tabela['opoznione_loty']
ind = np.arange(N)    # the x locations for the groups
width = 0.35       # the width of the bars: can also be len(x) sequence
plt.figure(figsize=(18,12))
p1 = plt.bar(ind, opoznienie, width, label='Liczba lotw', color='red')
p2 = plt.bar(ind, loty, width, bottom=opoznienie, label='Liczba lotw opnionych', color='blue', alpha=0.25)
plt.xticks(ind, (tabela.index), rotation=45, size=15)
plt.grid
plt.legend((p1[0], p2[0]), ('Delayed flights', 'Sum of flights'))
label = list(tabela['suma_lotow'].values)
labelpercent = list((100 - (tabela['opoznione_loty']/tabela['suma_lotow']*100)).astype(int))
for i in range(N):
    plt.text(x = i-0.17 , y = tabela['suma_lotow'][i]+10000, s=str(int(label[i]/1000))+'k', size = 12)
    plt.text(x = i-0.05 , y = tabela['suma_lotow'][i] - tabela['suma_lotow'][i]*0.30, s=str(labelpercent[i]) + '%', size = 11)
plt.title('Delays occurrence among the flight carrier', fontsize=15)
plt.show()
